# Styling (Uniwind)

## Conventions
- **Primary:** Use Uniwind classes for styling.
- **Avoid:** Inline styles (`style={{ ... }}`) whenever possible.
- **Syntax:** Ensure valid Tailwind class names compatible with the Uniwind configuration.
